# UI & Design

## Design Philosophy

- Minimalist and functional; French UI; responsive and accessible
- Colors: black on white; status colors for success/error/info
- Typography: Lato; consistent sizing and spacing (4px grid)
- Buttons radius 2px; forms/cards radius 4px; subtle shadows

## Global CSS

- Variables, reset, base, focus, utilities, forms, buttons, messages

## Layout

- `AppLayout`: wraps header/footer, global notifications, loading overlay
- `AppHeader`: responsive nav, auth-aware menu
- `AppFooter`: legal links, quick links, socials
- `BreadcrumbNav`: route-aware breadcrumb support

## Notifications and Loading

- `BaseNotification`: toast with types and auto-dismiss
- `BaseSpinner`: configurable spinner used globally
- Global notifications wired via `useUIStore`

## Cookie Consent and Policies

- `CookieBanner` for consent management
- `PolicyModal` to display policy content inline
